sequenceDiagram
    actor User as 用户（医师）
    participant UI as PrescribePage
    participant Ctx as PrescriptionContext
    participant Preload as window.electronAPI
    participant Main as Electron Main Process
    participant DB as DatabaseOperations
    participant Print as PrintHandler

    %% ===== 场景一：保存处方 =====

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over User,DB: 场景1：开具并保存处方（含 V2 变更）

        User->>UI: 填写患者信息（科别→下拉选择内科/外科）
        User->>UI: 填写诊断信息（处方编号自动生成）
        User->>UI: 添加药品（用量+用法 分两列填写）
        User->>UI: 填写医师信息（姓名非必填，科室→下拉选择）
        User->>UI: 点击「保存处方」

        UI->>Ctx: 读取 formData
        Ctx-->>UI: PrescriptionFormData

        UI->>UI: validatePrescriptionForm(formData)
        Note over UI: V2: doctor_name 不再校验必填

        UI->>UI: 构建 SavePrescriptionPayload
        Note over UI: medicines 每项含 usage_method

        UI->>Preload: savePrescription(payload)
        Preload->>Main: ipcMain.handle('db:save-prescription')
        Main->>DB: savePrescription(prescription, medicines)
        DB->>DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
        DB->>DB: INSERT prescriptions
        DB->>DB: INSERT prescription_medicines (含 usage_method)
        DB->>DB: COMMIT
        DB-->>Main: prescriptionId
        DB->>DB: getPrescriptionDetail(id)
        DB-->>Main: PrescriptionWithMedicines
        Main-->>Preload: result
        Preload-->>UI: PrescriptionWithMedicines

        UI->>Ctx: clearForm()
        Ctx-->>UI: 重置表单（保留处方编号）
        UI-->>User: Snackbar「处方 XXXX 保存成功」
    end

    %% ===== 场景二：打印预览 → 打印 =====

    rect rgb(255, 243, 230)
        Note over User,Print: 场景2：打印预览并确认打印（含 V2 变更）

        User->>UI: 点击「打印预览」
        UI->>UI: validatePrescriptionForm(formData)
        UI->>UI: 构建 PrescriptionWithMedicines
        UI->>UI: setPreviewData(data), setPreviewOpen(true)

        Note over UI: PreviewDialog 渲染 A5 处方笺
        Note over UI: 表头: 药品名称|规格|用量|用法|医嘱
        Note over UI: V2: doctor_name 为空显示 "____________"

        User->>UI: 点击「确认打印」
        UI->>Preload: printDirect(prescriptionData)
        Preload->>Main: ipcMain.handle('print:direct')
        Main->>Print: createPrintWindow(data)
        Print->>Print: generatePrescriptionHtml(data)
        Note over Print: V2: 用量+用法 分列渲染
        Note over Print: V2: 签名位空→"____________"
        Note over Print: V2: CSS width:148mm 严格A5
        Print->>Print: 创建隐藏 BrowserWindow
        Print->>Print: loadURL(data:...html)
        Print->>Print: webContents.print({pageSize:'A5'})
        Note over Print: 系统打印对话框弹出

        Print-->>User: 系统打印对话框（A5 纸张）
        User->>Print: 确认打印
        Print->>Print: 关闭隐藏窗口
        Print-->>Main: resolve()
        Main-->>Preload: void
        Preload-->>UI: void
        UI-->>User: 打印完成
    end

    %% ===== 场景三：历史查询 → 重新打印 =====

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over User,Print: 场景3：历史查询 — 查看详情并重新打印

        User->>UI: HistoryPage 搜索/浏览
        UI->>Preload: getPrescriptions(params)
        Preload->>Main: ipcMain.handle('db:get-prescriptions')
        Main->>DB: getPrescriptions(params)
        DB-->>Main: PaginatedResult~Prescription~
        Main-->>Preload: result
        Preload-->>UI: 处方列表

        User->>UI: 点击行 → 查看详情
        UI->>Preload: getPrescriptionDetail(id)
        Preload->>Main: ipcMain.handle('db:get-prescription-detail')
        Main->>DB: getPrescriptionDetail(id)
        DB-->>Main: PrescriptionWithMedicines (含 usage_method)
        Main-->>Preload: detail
        Preload-->>UI: PrescriptionWithMedicines

        Note over UI: PrescriptionDetail 对话框展示
        Note over UI: V2: 表头拆分为用量+用法
        Note over UI: V2: doctor_name 空→"____________"

        User->>UI: 点击「重新打印」
        UI->>UI: 关闭详情，打开预览
        Note over UI: 复用场景2的打印流程
    end
